description:
Jen Atkin covers SO much ground in this interview. To start? How to use Instagram to your advantage, dealing with jealousy, cutting bangs, Real Housewives, egg freezing, and way more. Before that: We talk Victoria Beckham and Fenty Beauty; Jess recounts her private hair tutorial; and we respond to some listener feedback.
